com.hoovler.dao.generic

Interface ProfileDao

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultProfileDao

    public interface ProfileDao

    ProfileDao

    Purpose This interface provides a basic outline for operations performed on a collection of Profile objects.

    Examples Instantiation using the DefaultProfileDao implementation: 

    ProfileDao profileDao = new DefaultProfileDao();
    Using a custom URI data source for the DefaultProfileDao implementation: 
     String dataSource = "http://your.custom.domain/apirofiles";
 ProfileDao profileDao = new DefaultProfileDao(dataSource);
